-- Saudi King Removes Adviser From Royal Court Position, SPA Says
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-05-12T07:56:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/saudi-king-removes-adviser-from-royal-court-position-spa-says.html
Saudi Arabia ’s King Abdullah removed
Sheikh Abdul Mohsen al-Obeikan from his position as adviser to
the Royal Court, the official  Saudi Press Agency  reported
yesterday, citing a Royal Decree.  The news service didn’t say why the Abdullah fired the
conservative cleric from his post.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
